snippet.title: Alpha Protocol - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Become Micahel Thornton in Alpha Protocol, the modern day espionage RPG - your weapon is choice. Every action has a consequence as you play, every path brings new decisions.

Choice can be a very deadly weapon, make sure you aren't killed by it.

Out today May 28th in Europe.
